<section id="how-it-works" class="py-20">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-8">
    <h2 class="text-4xl font-normal font-[Industry] text-pale-turquoise mb-12">
      > Your Journey to an Automated Business_
    </h2>

    <div class="mb-16">
      <!-- <h3 class="text-2xl font-normal text-pale-aqua mb-6">Imagine...</h3> -->
      <div class="space-y-4 text-lg font-light">
        <p>
          <strong class="text-pale-aqua font-medium"
            >Discovery & Strategy Call: </strong
          >We start with a free consultation to deeply understand your current workflows, pain points, and automation goals.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong class="text-pale-aqua font-medium"
            >Workflow Design & Proposal: </strong
          >Based on our discussion, we map out the proposed automation(s), detailing the scope, integrations, and expected outcomes with a clear proposal.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong class="text-pale-aqua font-medium"
            >Implementation & Rigorous Testing: </strong
          >Our experts build your custom automation workflows, ensuring they integrate seamlessly and function flawlessly through comprehensive testing.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong class="text-pale-aqua font-medium"
            >Deployment & Handover (Optional Training): </strong
          >We deploy the live automations and, if desired, provide training to your team on managing or monitoring them.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
